txt.en: Assisted the League of the Axe.
You have assisted the League of the Axe in their efforts throughout the Wildwood of Bree-land. All those in the League are thankful for your aid.
The League of the Axe is in need of assistance with efforts in the Wildwood of Bree-land.
Complete factionless quests in the Wildwood to assist the League of the Axe.

'The success of the League of the Axe is determined by each of its members, and we can ill-afford to be unprepared when the Wildwood is our only hope for a better life.\n\n'Aid the League of the Axe in our hardships, and I shall see that your efforts are rewarded.'
